【Universal Compatibility】 This 40W iPhone car charger adapter with usb-c to usb-c cable fast charging for iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max, New 2021 iPad Mini 6th Generation, 2021/2020/2018 iPad Pro 12.9 in 5th/4th/3rd Generation, iPad Pro 11 in 3rd/2nd/1st Generation(2021/2020/2018), iPad Air 4th generation (2020). 【Safety Efficient Fast Charging】 The iPhone 15 Pro Car Charger Fast Charging automatically recognizes dual devices, fills up safely, frees up more space, and provides you with a comfortable driving experience. Built-in multi-protection system, avoiding from over-voltage, over-charge, over-heat, etc., charge your iPhone/iPad device fast, safely and steadily.

【What You Get】 You will get 1 Pack 40W Dual USB C iPhone Fast Car Charger with 2 Pack 3.3FT USB C to USB C Fast Charging Data Sync Cable. body.description: Color: White Dual USB C Car Charger Fast Charging, 40W Dual Port USB C iPhone 15 Car Charger Adapter with 2 Pack USB C to USB C Cable. Car Charger USB C Specifications: Input Voltage: DC12-24V USB C PD 1 Output: 5V/3A, 9V/2.22A, 12V/1.67A USB C PD 2 Output: 5V/3A, 9V/2.22A, 12V/1.67A Total Output: 40W Max Universal Compatibility For iPhone/iPad iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max iPad Pro 12.9 5th/4th/3rd Generation 2021/2020/2018 iPad Pro 11 3rd/2nd/1st Generation 2021/2020/2018 iPad Air 4th Generation 2020 iPad mini 6th Generation 2021 For Android Phones Galaxy S23/S22/S21/S20/S10/S9/Note 20/10 Series Pixel 7/6/5/4/3/2 XL And more USB C devices. 4X Faster Charging Speed iPhone 15 fast car charger supports full-speed fast charging of two devices. Fast charging your iPhone 15 Pro Max up to 60% in 30mins. Safe and Fast Charging Multiple protections against over-current, overcharging, and overheating to ensure the safety of your devices. Charging will be automatically stopped when the battery is full. Compact and Durable Lightweight and highly portable, the tiny thumb-sized body fits most car cigarette lighters and barely protrudes past the edge of the outlet, providing a trim, less cluttered look. Blue LED Indicator With the user-friendly specifical design, soft blue LED indicator which is completely non-glaring helps locate the USB ports when charging in the dark. MFi Certified USB C to USB C Cable Built with MFi certified chip, build double protection for your devices. The 3.3ft iPhone 15 charger cable length allows you to charge your devices from an extra-long distance. What You Get 1 * 40W Dual USB C Car Charger 2 * 3.3FT MFi Certified USB C to USB C Cable A 3-Year Warranty and 24/7 Friendly Customer Service.
